casebody.data:
Lisa Anne HENRY, et al., petitioners,
v.
Brian WEISS, Liquidation Trustee of the Walldesign Liquidating Trust, Successor in Interest to the Official Committee of Unsecured Creditors of Walldesign, Inc. No. 17-1210. Supreme Court of the United States May 29, 2018.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
